Water Quality Data Summary
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Water quality samples were taken for the Watonwan CWP by Maple River CWP staff.
67 samples were collected at this site during the monitoring season.  
Sample distribution on Hydrograph:  Sample coverage was very good.  More rising limb samples and less baseline samples were needed.
TSS, TP, PO4, NO2+NO3-N, TKN, FC, Turbidity were analyzed using a laboratory.  
transparency tube were analyzed using field meter(s).  

